  <thing id="dCMEmpHeal" name="Empathic Healing" description="As a move action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity, you\ncan transfer the injuries of another creature to yourself with a touch. You transfer a maximum of 2 hit points per cleric level. No known mundane or magical protection can prevent you from taking the damage you transfer, and in any case your target only heals as much damage as you actually take. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your\nWisdom modifier." compset="ClSpecial">
