  <thing id="cCMSorcCry" name="Crystal" description="You have ties to supernatural forces of crystal and jewel. Perhaps you are descended from prognosticators who mingled with stone giants, or you may have been born adjacent to a crystal ball.\n\nBonus Spells: true strike (3rd), see invisibility (5th), arcane sight (7th), scrying (9th), contact other plane (11th), true seeing (13th), scrying, greater (15th), moment of prescience (17th), foresight (19th).\n\nBonus Feats: Alertness, Blind-Fight, Combat Casting, Deadly Aim, Dodge, Point-Blank Shot.\n\nBloodline Arcana: Whenever you cast a spell from the divination school you gain a luck bonus to all Perception and Sense Motive checks for ten minutes per spell level. This bonus is equal to the level of the spell cast.\n\nBloodline Powers: The scrying powers of crystal are yours to command, and your mastery of them leads to a growing ability to see the future." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
